## 4. File & Directory Location

âž¤ Use the **Explorer panel** or VS Code **Search (Ctrl+P or Cmd+P)** to locate files.
âœ³ï¸ If searching programmatically, write a utility or use `glob`, `fs`, or `os.walk` instead of shell commands.
âœ… Always refer to your project's root (e.g., `./src`, not `/repo/` or absolute paths).

## 5. Database Debugging (PostgreSQL)

âž¤ Use tools like:

